    "description": {
      "en": {
        "provenance": "imported",
        "value": "The proposed fund shall be utilised to procure the required steel parts including steel decks, anchorage parts, gabion mesh etc. required to rehabilitate the ‘critical’ trail bridges. SDC will procure the materials through a local bidding procedure and hand over the materials to the respective District Development Committees (DDC). The Trail Bridge Support Unit managed by Helvetas shall provide all the required technical and administrative support to SDC.\r\n\r\n\t \r\n\r\n\tDistricts are the main implementers at the operational level. Once they receive the steel parts from SDC, they shall allocate adequate budget for labour and other materials such as cement, sand and aggregate. It is also the responsibility of the DDC to organise the contribution from communities wherever applicable. All other approaches concerning social inclusion, transparency and governance, conflict sensitivity, insurance of labour, timely payments, steering, monitoring etc will be applied as usual"
      },
      "ne": null
    },
